readBytes(InputStream, byte[]) - Static method in class org.stringmatching.utils.IOUtils
Reads bytes from an InputStream into the byte array, until the byte array is filled or there are no more bytes in the stream.
readBytes(RandomAccessFile, byte[]) - Static method in class org.stringmatching.utils.IOUtils
Reads bytes from a RandomAccessFile into the byte array, starting from the current seek position of the RandomAccessFile, until the byte array is filled or there are no more bytes in the RandomAccessFile.
readBytes(RandomAccessFile, byte[], long) - Static method in class org.stringmatching.utils.IOUtils
Reads bytes from a RandomAccessFile into the byte array, starting from the position provided in the RandomAccessFile, until the byte array is filled or there are no more bytes in the RandomAccessFile.
readEntireFile(File) - Static method in class org.stringmatching.utils.IOUtils
Reads the bytes in a file into a single byte array and returns it.
readEntireStream(InputStream) - Static method in class org.stringmatching.utils.IOUtils
Reads an input stream and returns a single array of bytes containing the stream contents.
resetResults() - Method in class org.stringmatching.matcher.Matcher
